headline: ICE Launches MSCI® MarketAxess Tradable Corporate Bond Index Futures to Help Investors Hedge Corporate Bond Exposure
summary: NEW YORK & LONDON, December 12, 2024--Intercontinental Exchange, Inc. (NYSE: ICE), a leading global provider of technology and data, and home to the most liquid markets for trading MSCI® futures, today announced the launch of MSCI® MarketAxess Tradable Corporate Bond Index futures.
